     <ftp://tsx-11.mit.edu/pub/linux/ALPHA/scanner/scan-
     driver-0.1.8.tar.gz>

    Mustek HT800 Turbo, Matador 105, Matador 256 handheld scanners
     <ftp://tsx-11.mit.edu/pub/linux/ALPHA/scanner/scan-
     driver-0.1.8.tar.gz>

