     <ftp://sunsite.unc.edu/pub/Linux/apps/graphics/capture/muscan-2.0.6.taz>

    Nikon Coolscan SCSI 35mm film scanner
     <ftp://sunsite.unc.edu/pub/Linux/apps/graphics/capture/coolscan-0.2.tgz>

