     <ftp://tsx-11.mit.edu/pub/linux/ALPHA/scanner/umax-0.5.5.tar.gz>

  The Mustek drivers work only with GI1904 interface cards. Eric Chang
  eric.chang@chrysalis.org has created a patch to use them with IF960
  interface cards.


